he Bureau's new squad, Black Torch, and help them battle powerful mononoke who seek to devour innocent people.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]","streaming":[{"name":"Crunchyroll","url":"https://www.crunchyroll.com/"}],"type":"TV","genres":["Action","Supernatural"]},{"id":59741,"title":"Tsuihou sareta Tensei Juukishi wa Game Chishiki de Musou suru","title_english":"The Exiled Heavy Knight Knows How to Game the System","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-07-03T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1690/155778l.jpg","synopsis":"\"You useless son of mine! You were supposed to pull master swordsman, but I never thought it would be this tragic!\"\n\nThe day a child turns fifteen, they undergo the Ritual of Divine Blessing. Already descended from a line of master swordsman, Elymas was supposed to succeed his father. However, he pulls the defective class, the Heavy Knight, and not only loses his status as future head of the household, but he's also exiled. With their unbalanced stats and seemingly useless skills, Heavy Knights are spoked of as a class for cowards and the lazy. However, Elymas knows the truth. The world he lives in is the same as the one of the game he used to play... It is the Heavy Knight that is the most powerful class of them all. Using memories from his past life, Elymas has set out to effectively conquer this entire world.\n\n(Source: Kodansha USA)","streaming":[{"name":"Crunchyroll","url":"https://www.crunchyroll.com"}],"type":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"]},{"id":46488,"title":"Tai-Ari deshita. Ojousama wa Kakutou Game nante Shinai","title_english":"Young Ladies Don't Play Fighting Games","episodes":0,"score":0,"start_date":"2026-07-07T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1343/156268l.jpg","synopsis":"A hot fighting game played at the girls' school!!\n\nAya transferred into Kuromi Girls Academy a month ago with the goal of changing herself into 